</p>

<p>Profiles Research Networking Software is available as an <a href="http://connects.catalyst.harvard.edu/Profiles/about/default.aspx?tab=open" target="_blank">open source platform</a> for institutions seeking a web-based means of facilitating collaboration among their academic researchers. </p>  

